      "description": "Offered for sale is a dependable vehicle in good condition, perfect for someone looking for a well-maintained daily driver. Mechanically, the engine is strong and the car handles smoothly on the road. The interior is clean and has been cared for, showing only minimal signs of use. On the exterior, the paint retains a healthy shine, though a careful inspection will reveal some minor road rash on the front bumper and a few small door dings. Overall, it is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner.",
