    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every facet, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects meticulous care and uncompromising maintenance standards. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of such distinguished caliber, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original debut.",
