    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously won't believe how gorgeous this car is until you see it in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered with regular detailing. It honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch, dent, or worry! I\u2019m only parting with it because our family is growing, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely cherish it. Come give it a spin, you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
