    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance, featuring the iconic S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a flawlessly functioning double-VANOS system. The power delivery is linear and high-revving, paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock for maximum traction. The chassis is structurally immaculate, featuring a reinforced subframe and factory-spec bushings that preserve the platform's legendary communicative steering and 50/50 weight distribution. Every mechanical component, from the cooling system to the suspension geometry, remains in peak operating condition, offering a tactile and visceral driving experience that defines the golden era of M-division engineering.",
